problem are chosen as ν = 1.0 and σ = 1.0. In the case of convection dominated ﬂow (i.e. for small ν), the tangential components disappear as they scale with ν, and eﬀectively the same formulation as presented and studied in [2] is retained. For this reason, we focus on investigating viscous ﬂows here. As the pressure is only deﬁned up to a constant, the constant pressure mode is ﬁltered out by imposing Ω phdx = 0 during the solution process.
